:''Tamayt i Yakuc, mass n umeɣrad''
:''Amellay amnahaɣ''
:''Agellid n wass n wesɣan''
:''D keč  i nettmudu, ɣur-ek la ntetter tullin''
:''Welleh-aɣ s abrid amaɣud''
