:''Amin'''

Amedya wayeḍ, d anza, umi qaren s teɛrabt ''El-ixlaṣ'', asnuquel ar taqbaylit, mačči d win : ''Qul Huwa Llahu Aḥed''. Yernu am Lfattiḥa, imesla-s d taɛrabt. A tnan : 
 
